---

KarbonLens aggregates and presents public data about voluntary carbon
market projects. Upstream data sources retain their own copyrights and
terms of use:

  - Verra (verra.org)
  - Gold Standard (goldstandard.org)
  - Puro.earth (puro.earth)
  - American Carbon Registry / ACR (americancarbonregistry.org)
  - Climate Action Reserve / CAR (climateactionreserve.org)
  - Global Forest Watch / GLAD-S2 (globalforestwatch.org)

The aggregated dataset compiled by the KarbonLens project is made
available under CC BY 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/).
Attribution to upstream registries is preserved in project records.

Third-party open-source dependencies are listed in package.json and
licensed under their respective terms. See node_modules/<pkg>/LICENSE
for each.
